```go
names := []string{"go", "rust", "zig"}
for _, n := range names {
    n = strings.ToUpper(n)
}
fmt.Println(names)
```

下面代码的输出是什么？
```go
type Score struct { Val int }
scores := []Score{{10}, {20}, {30}}
for i := range scores {
    scores[i].Val *= 2
}
fmt.Println(scores)
```
